platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: The fabulous Bloons series has always been a colorful and clever spin on the tower-defense genre. When youre up against human opponents in Bloons TD Battles, though, youd better be as sharp as a blimp-bursting tack. Dont be fooled by the mischievous monkeysthis is a game of riveting strategy and intense head-to-head hijinks.
